Amsterdam hosted today a working meeting between Alexey Miller , Chairman of the Gazprom Management Committee and Andrey Kobolev , CEO of Naftogaz of Ukraine .
It was urged at the meeting that the Ukrainian party should settle the debt for Russian gas supplied in 2013 and 2014 .

Gazprom will be delivering strictly prepaid amounts of gas to Ukraine , starting from June .
